								<!-- Step 6 -->
								<div class="flex gap-3 items-start bg-slate-900/30 border border-white/[0.03] p-3 rounded-xl">
									<span class="bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 font-mono font-bold text-xs w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-emerald-500/20 flex-shrink-0">6</span>
									<div>
										<h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Dashboard Refresh & Sound Alert</h4>
										<p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">This browser UI queries the API server (running on port <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono">8081</code>) every 3 seconds. When a new email file is detected, it plays a bell audio notification (<code class="text-gray-300 font-mono">bell.wav</code>) and renders the message instantly.</p>
									</div>
